FINAL GROUP PROJECT
Digital Margiela
Athira & Antwaan

Core:

Fashion magazine
Fashion magazine app that has all the vintage fashion magazines and articles you can read with a zine that gets sent to your house every month. Accept and publish more new stuff.

PROBLEM STATEMENT:
There are around 80 fashion-based magazines worldwide. Trying to buy some of these magazines would of course cost too much, and what about the old issues they don't produce anymore? With our app, we can send copies of vintage magazines of your choice!

SOLUTION:
Our MVP is an app that allows users to browse through and read different vintage and current magazines. You are able to access more from the app. The app will include magazines from different brands. As well as a zine that gets sent to your house every month. And a place for young, new aspiring artists to upload their own magazines for others to indulge.

TARGET MARKET:
Our target audience would be those who love everything fashion and would like to learn more about the industry. As well as vintage collectors. Around 200 million people still read magazines, so realistically possibly around 50-100 million people.

WHY ITS VALUABLE:
Digital Margiela is valuable because it gives fashion lovers, students, collectors, and creatives access to magazines that are often expensive, hard to find, or no longer in production. Instead of searching through different websites or paying high resale prices, users can explore a curated digital archive and receive physical copies delivered directly to them. The platform also creates opportunities for new and upcoming artists to showcase their own work, helping build a stronger creative community while keeping magazine culture alive in a modern digital format. 

HOW YOU'LL MAKE MONEY:
This will be a subscription-based app.

MVP FEATURES:
Monthly Subscription system
Magazine Delivery
Digital Archive of Magazines
